Well - I don't know whether they were getting on then - or whether it was - that she wanted to put the best side to London, but we - never - we never heard the word like mortgage, that's - very comm
on sort of talk. Never - and he must have - given mortgages to hundreds of people, but he never - we - we never talked of - we didn't know whose house was mortgaged and whose was paid for. I mean it's very common to talk about your mortgage don't you. No.
 
No. Oh well they did have a mortgage - but they had it with one person didn't they. The lawyer arranged a mortgage with a wealthy man. But I don't think they had these - Buildings Societies. And - I don't know whether they're money making or whether they'
re good for the people. Do you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4873271\charrsid8088101 They are supposed to be non profit making aren't they?
