\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2824748 MR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4873271\charrsid8088101 Well I think - we were just a family and that's it. I don't think - well there were no worries in a way were there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4873271\charrsid8088101 But how did your father and mother expect you to behave towards them, the girls and your adopted brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2824748 MR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4873271\charrsid8088101 Oh I think just ordinary don't you.
