Well it depended. My mother and father didn't dance. But Ori danced. And a friend perhaps of my mother's or father's would take us. You know, with their children. But I think they - brought us up very protected and we were very pro
tected until we were a pretty good age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4873271\charrsid8088101 Until how old do you think?
