\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4873271\charrsid8088101  God}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1858084\charrsid8088101 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4873271\charrsid8088101 fearing upright home. And - never do a shabby trick.
