\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2824748 MR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4873271\charrsid8088101 Never. Good heavens no, we were banished. Sent in the kitchen to do something or sent to the - breakfast r
oom to go and read a book or - and we were never allowed to put our tongue into things. Not until we were grown up you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid861 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4873271\charrsid8088101 Never allowed to join in a conversation?
